{"tid":474041,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀Psychology","createTime":"2017-11-19T19:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T19:48:38.000Z","uid":137885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bc71076f8a2e391fae85a5e803793aa8d952b46d","tid":474041,"uid":137885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:15:05.000Z","msg":"有冇人同我一樣讀Psychology讀到好乏力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔知可以點溫書 Evaluation等等個啲長問題完全唔識點樣答 就算我睇明晒啲theory之後都好似冇乜幫助 <br />\n<br />\n讀到覺得自己好廢 就算有溫書都考到成pat屎咁<br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人可以分享下經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：讀緊A-Level Psychology <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2d9679d17227d98368646f049fbe3124f9c1ef","tid":474041,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:33:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fe6ed1bad218618354329a57b4bf3449036da49","tid":474041,"uid":137885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>There are lots of revision materials online.<br />\n<br />\nSample:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/20/033324_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F20%2F033324_7fffb663120dd173020ed4b9bc223583.jpg&h=fb5f68f1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個board冇mc題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  得short同long questions<br />\nShort question 因為考concept 所以都ok<br />\n但long question 真係唔知點寫 可能自己英文差 唔識寫essay <br />\n又唔知點溫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係都多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45ef7abb844753b86d4bf1c7153476e6e99fb55","tid":474041,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:48:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}